Package: epics-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-libs, epics-perl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: epics-doc
Description: Files needed to develop new EPICS applications
 Libraries, headers, and utilities needed to develop applications
 targeted to the host system.

Package: epics-compat-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-dev, epics-libs, epics-perl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: epics-doc
Description: Files needed to develop new EPICS applications
 Libraries, headers, and utilities needed to develop applications
 targeted to the host system.
 This package contains additional files needed for compatibility with EPICS 3.13.x

